snippet.title: Plazma Burst 2 gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Plazma Burst 2 is a free-to-play tactical 2D shooter game, it is a sequel to a game called Plazma Burst: Forward to the Past

Game developed by Eric Gurt, sponsored by Coolbuddy.com . Music which is used in this trailer is made by Nphonix.

Official game website is here:
http://www.PlazmaBurst2.com
